transcript:
[No transcript available]
Customer: Hello?\n
Executive: Hello?\n
Customer: Sir, main ek cheez aur puch raha tha, aapne hame call kara hua tha na?\n
Executive: Ji.\n
Customer: To us call ke related hamare paas mein missed call ka notification aaya hua tha.\n
Executive: Achcha.\n
Customer: To aap missed call ka notification close kar rahe hain. Aapke paas mein feedback ke liye jayega, please aap feedback zarur share kijiyega.\n
Executive: Theek hai.\n
Customer: Mean while sir, ek baar ko na ye saari cheeze karte hain, phir we need to discuss on services as well.\n
Executive: Theek hai.\n
Customer: Hai na? To please jitna jaldi ho sakta hai, aap please hame mail kar dijiye. So that phir hum aage ki cheeze isko proceed kar paaye. Services vagarah bhi use ho nahi rahi hai.\n
Executive: Ji.\n
Customer: Right?\n
Customer: To ek baar ko wo saari cheeze bhi hame check karni hai.\n
Executive: Theek hai.\n
Customer: Okay sir. Thank you sir.\n
